nd round\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 328}, {\"ngram\": \"such astronomical success\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 406}, {\"ngram\": \"his phenomenal career\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, with injury problems and a reduced schedule over the last couple of years, Nadal says Djokovic will be expected to beat him, given he is still ranked at number two in the world, while the King of Clay is down at 161.\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 520, \"end\": 525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7767321997563744e-17, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 531, \"end\": 539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.590860924130438e-14, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"injury problems\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 465}, {\"ngram\": \"a reduced schedule\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 488}, {\"ngram\": \"the last couple\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 518}, {\"ngram\": \"number\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 604}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 621}, {\"ngram\": \"the King\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"Clay\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Situations are completely different for him, for me,' said Nadal.\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 723, \"end\": 728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7767321997563744e-17, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Situations\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'He's being very competitive.\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 759, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was not being very competitive for the last two years, so in that case, I think probably he is the clear favourite.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last two years\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 815}, {\"ngram\": \"that case\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am going to try my best to bring the best to the court and then let us see how far I can go and how many problems I can create for him.'\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"how many problems\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal holds an 8-2 record over Djokovic at Roland Garros and is relishing the chance to meet him again at the iconic venue, even if it is in the unusual setting of a second round.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.590860924130438e-14, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 1063, \"end\": 1076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.999984943878984, \"rank\": 1.5056303433364875e-05, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Na